original_title: Sebelum Dunia Terbalik: Tragedi Cinta Kemed Dan Eros
overview: Kemed who was hurt by Eros three years earlier. A few days before the wedding between Eros and Joseph. Kemed who saw the invitation still think of Eros who will marry Joseph his friend, while in cibarengkong the youth bet who the future husband of Eros. With various efforts finally kemed managed to meet Eros. Finally because of his great love for Eros he decided to kidnap Eros.
title: Sebelum Dunia Terbalik: Tragedi Cinta Kemed Dan Eros
